=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies the placement details for the node in the SageMaker HyperPod
cluster, including the Availability Zone and the unique identifier (ID)
of the Availability Zone.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AvailabilityZone => Str

The Availability Zone where the node in the SageMaker HyperPod cluster
is launched.


=head2 AvailabilityZoneId => Str

The unique identifier (ID) of the Availability Zone where the node in
the SageMaker HyperPod cluster is launched.



